  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "g8klaFHNxA86PjJRrpT553RKOQM=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# resource-template model defines reusable service catalog blueprints\n\n`powerhouse/resource-template` defines the base configuration that ServiceOfferings build on. Templates provide the service catalog structure without pricing.\n\n## State Shape\n\n```graphql\ntype ResourceTemplateState {\n    id: PHID!\n    operatorId: PHID!              # \u2192 BuilderProfile (external)\n    title: String!\n    summary: String!\n    status: TemplateStatus!        # DRAFT | COMING_SOON | ACTIVE | DEPRECATED\n    targetAudiences: [TargetAudience!]!\n    setupServices: [String!]!\n    recurringServices: [String!]!\n    facetTargets: [FacetTarget!]!\n    services: [Service!]!\n    optionGroups: [OptionGroup!]!\n    faqFields: [FaqField!]\n    contentSections: [ContentSection!]!\n}\n```\n\n## Modules (7)\n\n| Module | Operations | Purpose |\n|--------|-----------|---------|\n| template-management | 4 | Info, status, operator, ID |\n| audience-management | 2 | Add/remove target audiences |\n| facet-targeting | 4 | Set/remove facet targets, add/remove options |\n| service-category-management | 2 | Set setup/recurring service lists |\n| service-management | 5 | Service CRUD, facet bindings |\n| option-group-management | 3 | Option group CRUD |\n| content-section-management | 3+3 | Content sections + FAQ CRUD |\n\n## Key References\n\n- `operatorId: PHID` \u2192 BuilderProfile (external)\n- `Service.parentServiceId: OID` \u2192 Service (self-referencing hierarchy)\n- `Service.optionGroupId: OID` \u2192 OptionGroup\n- `facetBindings.facetType: PHID` \u2192 Facet (this project)\n- ServiceOffering.`resourceTemplateId` \u2192 references this model\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[schema design]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:43.000Z"
    }
  },
